<translation id="2329130305935541101">I-WEB3 DNA Browser ithole ukuthi i-"<ph name="EXTENSION_NAME" />" inohlelo olungayilungele ikhompyutha</translation>
<translation id="2947483933825476413">I-WEB3 DNA Browser ibuyekeziwe, kodwa awukakayisebenzisi okungenani izinsuku ezingu-30.</translation>
<translation id="8828344991758417694">I-WEB3 DNA Browser idinga ukufinyelela kwe-Bluetooth ukuze iqhubeke 
 nokumatanisa. <ph name="IDS_BLUETOOTH_DEVICE_CHOOSER_AUTHORIZE_BLUETOOTH_LINK" /></translation>
<translation id="9067852028442542655">Lapho imizamo ivuliwe, Isilinganiso sesikhangiso sivumela amasayithi owavakashelayo ukuba acele ulwazi ku-WEB3 DNA Browser olusiza isayithi ukukala ukusebenza kwezikhangiso zawo. Isilinganiso sesikhangiso sikhawulela ukulandelela indawo yonke ngokudlulisa ulwazi oluncane ngangokunokwenzeka phakathi kwamasayithi.</translation>
<translation id="6638774777596425412">Kamuva, isayithi olivakashelayo lingacela i-WEB3 DNA Browser ukuthi ibone izintshisekelo zakho ukuze yenze izikhangiso ozibonayo ngokwezifiso zakho. I-WEB3 DNA Browser ikwazi ukwabelana ngezintshisekelo ezifika ku-3.</translation>
<translation id="1618581910910744310">Vula isixhumanisi kuwindi le-WEB3 DNA Browser inco&amp;gnito</translation>
<translation id="1141174083986936166">Amaphasiwedi angaqinile aqageleka kalula. Vumela i-WEB3 DNA Browser <ph name="BEGIN_LINK" />ikudalele futhi ikhumbule amaphasiwedi aqinile<ph name="END_LINK" />.</translation>
