<translation id="7025789849649390912">Ukufaka Kumisiwe.</translation>
<translation id="475843105037256922">Buyekeza i-WEB3 DNA Browser</translation>
<translation id="326486748351990910">Uma isithombe singanayo incazelo ephelele, i-WEB3 DNA Browser izozama ukukunikezela eyodwa. Ukuze udale izincazelo, izithombe zithunyelwa ku-Google.</translation>
<translation id="5618043080831675837">I-WEB3 DNA Browser idinga imvume yekhamera kule sayithi</translation>
<translation id="6831720849639347633">Ayikwazanga ukuqalisa i-WEB3 DNA Browser. Zama futhi.</translation>
<translation id="7914905542208857296">I-WEB3 DNA Browser ayikwazi ukuhlola iphasiwedi yakho. Zama futhi emva kwamahora angu-24.</translation>
<translation id="2219572028161280443">Amasayithi owavakashelayo akhumbula ulwazi lwakho uze uvale i-WEB3 DNA Browser</translation>
<translation id="3988179273882088670">Isiphathi somsebenzi - I-WEB3 DNA Browser</translation>
<translation id="8082426603469914763">Izintshisekelo zakho njengoba zilinganiselwe yi-WEB3 DNA Browser</translation>
<translation id="3791422786486318548">Isilinganiso sesikhangiso sivumela amasayithi owavakashelayo ukuba acele ulwazi ku-WEB3 DNA Browser olusiza isayithi ukukala ukusebenza kwezikhangiso zawo. Isilinganiso sesikhangiso sikhawulela ukulandelela indawo yonke ngokudlulisa ulwazi oluncane ngangokunokwenzeka phakathi kwamasayithi.</translation>
<translation id="3826673197841439968">Ibuyekeza i-WEB3 DNA Browser</translation>
<translation id="3105300744480734014">Ifayela lakho lokuncamelayo limoshakele noma alivumelekile.

I-WEB3 DNA Browser ayikwazi ukubuyisela izilungiselelo zakho.</translation>
<translation id="4691707200828155405">WEB3 DNA Browser</translation>
<translation id="7339898014177206373">Iwindi elisha</translation>
<translation id="866415121309420782">Iwebhu yakho, amabhukhimakhi, nezinye izinto ze-WEB3 DNA Browser zihlala lapha.</translation>
<translation id="2516718275146731816">Umlawuli wakho wesistimu ulungiselele i-WEB3 DNA Browser ukuthi ivule i-<ph name="ALTERNATIVE_BROWSER_NAME" /> ukuze ifinyelele ku-<ph name="TARGET_URL_HOSTNAME" />.</translation>
<translation id="5218043865814307173">Ngamaphrofayela we-WEB3 DNA Browser ungahlukanisa zonke izinto zakho ze-WEB3 DNA Browser. Lokhu kwenza kube lula ukuhlukanisa phakathi komsebenzi nokuzijabulisa.</translation>
<translation id="5690617926609878272"><ph name="PAGE_TITLE" /> - WEB3 DNA Browser Dev</translation>
<translation id="3479625329890795142">I-WEB3 DNA Browser idinga imvume yakho ukuze ifinyelele kukhamera yakho yaleli sayithi</translation>
<translation id="3327138471292503109">Ukuze uthole izibuyekezo zesikhathi esizayo ze-WEB3 DNA Browser, uzodinga i-Windows 10 noma yakamuva. Le khompyutha isebenzisa i-Windows 7.</translation>
<translation id="570029382864869633">Qalisa kabusha i-WEB3 DNA Browser?</translation>
<translation id="7081567920020845898">Ayikwazi ukufaka inguqulo ye-WEB3 DNA Browser efana nale esebenzayo okwamanje. Sicela uvale i-WEB3 DNA Browser uphinde uzame futhi.</translation>
<translation id="2308694661846361163">{0,plural, =1{I-WEB3 DNA Browser izoqalisa kabusha kuminithi elingu-1}one{I-WEB3 DNA Browser izoqalisa kabusha emaminithini angu-#}other{I-WEB3 DNA Browser izoqalisa kabusha emaminithini angu-#}}</translation>
<translation id="7403013663461228352">Futhi sula idatha kusuka ku-WEB3 DNA Browser (<ph name="URL" />)</translation>
<translation id="5628570284195611526">I-WEB3 DNA Browser ingasikisela izintshisekelo zakho. Kamuva, isayithi olivakashelayo lingacela i-WEB3 DNA Browser ukuthi ibone izintshisekelo zakho ukuze yenze izikhangiso ozibonayo ngokwezifiso zakho.</translation>
<translation id="7583399374488819119">Isifaki Se-<ph name="COMPANY_NAME" /></translation>
<translation id="18937021822671718">Uvule Ukuphequlula Ngokuphepha Okugqamile ku-akhawunti yakho. Manje yitholele i-WEB3 DNA Browser.</translation>
<translation id="2422729508884289622">I-WEB3 DNA Browser isebenzisa ikhamela yakho nemakrofoni.</translation>
<translation id="7649176261008984828">I-WEB3 DNA Browser ibe ngcono nakakhulu</translation>
<translation id="7649070708921625228">Usizo</translation>
<translation id="5663191066657660868">Ungafunda kabanzi mayelana nalezi zakhi kumasethingi we-WEB3 DNA Browser.</translation>
<translation id="1180711544607099420">I-WEB3 DNA Browser ihlola izakhi ezintsha ezivumela amasayithi ukuthi alethe ukuzizwisa kokubhrawuza okufanayo kusetshenziswa idatha yakho encane</translation>
<translation id="1427927054102592884">I-WEB3 DNA Browser akusona isiphequluli sakho esizenzakalelayo</translation>
<translation id="7195845268083706212">Vumelanisa uphinde wenze kube ngeyakho i-WEB3 DNA Browser kumadivayisi akho wonkana</translation>
<translation id="4540014860380760179">Lokhu kuzosusa idatha yakho yokuphequlula kusukela kule divayisi. Ukuze uthole idatha yakho emuva kwesikhathi, ngena ngemvume ku-WEB3 DNA Browser njengo-<ph name="USER_EMAIL" />.</translation>
<translation id="7747138024166251722">Isifaki asikwazanga ukudala umkhombandlela wesikhashana. Sicela uhlolele isikhala esikhululekile sediski nemvume ukuze ufake isofthiwe.</translation>
<translation id="3341158123816213810">Yenza i-WEB3 DNA Browser isheshe</translation>
