<translation id="8502268940781535829">Iphrofayela ye-WEB3 DNA Browser enale akhawunti isikhona akakade kule divayisi</translation>
<translation id="7845233973568007926">Siyabonga ngokufaka. Kufanele uqalise kabusha ikhompyutha yakho ngaphambi kokusebenzisa i-<ph name="BUNDLE_NAME" />.</translation>
<translation id="5422417406245013307">I-WEB3 DNA Browser ayikwazanga ukubuyekezela kwinguqulo yakamuva, ngakho-ke uyalahlekelwa kuzici ezintsha nokulungiswa kokuphepha.</translation>
<translation id="7872446069773932638">Iyadawuniloda... kusele imizuzwana engu-<ph name="SECONDS" /></translation>
<translation id="6590823489474620893"><ph name="BEGIN_BOLD" />Ungayiphatha kanjani idatha yakho:<ph name="END_BOLD" /> Ukuze sivikele ubumfihlo bakho, sisula ngokuzenzakalelayo izintshisekelo zakho ezindala kunamaviki ama-4. Njengoba uqhubeka nokubhrawuza, intshisekelo ingase ivele ohlwini futhi. Noma ungasusa izithakazelo ongafuni ukuthi i-WEB3 DNA Browser izicabangele.</translation>
<translation id="7280500878215405781">Ubukade ungene ngemvume ku-WEB3 DNA Browser njengo-<ph name="USER_EMAIL_ADDRESS" />. Sicela usebenzise i-akhawunti efanayo ukuze uphinde ungene ngemvume futhi.</translation>
<translation id="2253021454574730566">Lokhu ukufakwa kwesibili kwe-WEB3 DNA Browser, futhi akukwazi ukwenziwa isiphequluli sakho esizenzakalelayo.</translation>
<translation id="2180063386451170761">Izandiso, ama-app, namatimu asuka emithonjeni engaziwa angalimaza idivayisi yakho. I-WEB3 DNA Browser incoma ukuzifaka kuphela zisuka ku-<ph name="IDS_EXTENSION_WEB_STORE_TITLE" /></translation>
<translation id="1446133009793910887">Uma i-WEB3 DNA Browser inokufinyelela, amawebhusayithi azokwazi ukukucela ukufinyelela.</translation>
<translation id="80471789339884597">Siyabonga ngokufaka. Kufanele uqalise kabusha wonke amabhrawuza akho ngaphambi kokusebenzisa i-<ph name="BUNDLE_NAME" />.</translation>
<translation id="3869525261991846539">I-WEB3 DNA Browser idinga imvume yendawo kule sayithi</translation>
<translation id="8133124826068723441">I-ChromiumOS ayikwazanga ukuvumelanisa idatha yakho ngoba Ukuvumelanisa akutholakali kusizinda sakho.</translation>
<translation id="813913629614996137">Iyaqalisa...</translation>
<translation id="6871375725780252705">Leli fayela liyingozi, ngakho-ke i-WEB3 DNA Browser iyivimbile.</translation>
<translation id="8821717781402291672">I-WEB3 DNA Browser ivimbe leli fayela ngoba lolu hlobo lwefayela luyingozi</translation>
<translation id="8394136310056741303">Uma isithombe singanayo incazelo ephelele, i-WEB3 DNA Browser izozama ukukunikezela eyodwa. Ukuze udale izincazelo, izithombe zithunyelwa ku-Google. Ungavala lokhu kuzilungiselelo noma kunini.</translation>
<translation id="4863557335992202213">I-WEB3 DNA Browser ayikwazi ukuhlola amaphasiwedi akho ngoba awungenanga ngemvume</translation>
<translation id="8332908002682218419">I-WEB3 DNA Browser izama ukukopisha amaphasiwedi.</translation>
<translation id="3862328687893385239">Leli fayela lingaba yingozi, ngakho-ke i-WEB3 DNA Browser iyivimbile.</translation>
<translation id="7450630974943556627">Ngena ngemvume ukuze uvumelanise uphinde wenze kube ngeyakho i-WEB3 DNA Browser kumadivayisi akho wonkana</translation>
<translation id="8910359951607649198"><ph name="USER_EMAIL_ADDRESS" /> ngaphambilini ibisebenzisa i-WEB3 DNA Browser</translation>
<translation id="7837286795552251352">Ukuze ufinyelele ezintweni zakho ze-browser ye-WEB3 DNA Browser kuwo wonke amadivayisi wakho, ngena ngemvume, bese uvula ukuvumelanisa</translation>
<translation id="4231941262737361466">Ukuze uthole izibuyekezo zesikhathi esizayo ze-WEB3 DNA Browser, uzodinga i-Windows 10 noma yakamuva. Le khompyutha isebenzisa i-Windows 8.</translation>
<translation id="4708615805477131870">{0,plural, =1{Qalisa kabusha i-WEB3 DNA Browser phakathi kosuku}one{Qalisa kabusha i-WEB3 DNA Browser phakathi kwezinsuku ezingu-#}other{Qalisa kabusha i-WEB3 DNA Browser phakathi kwezinsuku ezingu-#}}</translation>
<translation id="8293407095466346653">Ingobo yomlando yesifaki yonakele noma ayivumelekile. Sicela ulande futhi i-WEB3 DNA Browser.</translation>
<translation id="8463672209299734063">Ongakukhetha: Siza ekuthuthukiseni izakhi nokusebenza kwe-ChromiumOS ngokuthumela ngokuzenzekelayo idatha yokusetshenziswa neyokuxilonga ku-Google.</translation>
<translation id="2275026549113043779">I-WEB3 DNA Browser ayikho kudethi</translation>
<translation id="8550334526674375523">Le phrofayela yomsebenzi ihluke ngokugcwele kusukela kuphrofayela yakho siqu.</translation>
<translation id="3829194378861761606">Umzali wakho uvale "Izimvume zamasayithi, izinhlelo zokusebenza, nezandiso" ze-WEB3 DNA Browser. Ukwengeza le <ph name="EXTENSION_TYPE_PARAMETER" /> akuvumelekile.</translation>
<translation id="6148620910029690666">Ukuze uthole izibuyekezo zesikhathi esizayo ze-WEB3 DNA Browser, uzodinga i-macOS 10.13 noma eyakamuva. Le khompyutha isebenzisa i-macOS 10.12.</translation>
<translation id="1246723111619277441">I-WEB3 DNA Browser ingahlola amaphasiwedi akho uma ungena ngemvume nge-Akhawunti yakho ye-Google</translation>
<translation id="7115352036028984404">Uma ivuliwe, i-WEB3 DNA Browser igcina amandla ebhethri ngokukhawulela umsebenzi ongemuva nemiphumela yokubuka, njengokuskrola okubushelelezi namazinga ozimele wevidiyo. <ph name="BEGIN_LINK" />Funda kabanzi<ph name="END_LINK" /></translation>
<translation id="4799188800355420938">Copyright <ph name="YEAR" /> Ababhali be-WEB3 DNA Browser. Wonke amalungelo agciniwe.</translation>
<translation id="1392803118131207008"><ph name="BEGIN_BOLD" />Indlela esisebenzisa ngayo le datha:<ph name="END_BOLD" /> Amasayithi angagcina ulwazi nge-WEB3 DNA Browser mayelana nezintshisekelo zakho. Ngokwesibonelo, uma uvakashela isayithi ukuze uthenge izicathulo zomjaho webanga elide, isayithi lingachaza intshisekelo yakho njengokugijima umjaho. Kamuva, uma uvakashela isayithi elihlukile ukuze ubhalisele umjaho, lelo sayithi lingakubonisa isikhangiso sezicathulo zokugijima ezisekelwe kuzintshisekelo zakho.</translation>
<translation id="5546249279042208244">Iqalisa i-WEB3 DNA Browser...</translation>
<translation id="5255237181758616742">Ukufakwa kuhlulekile ngenxa yephutha elingacacisiwe. Sicela ulande i-WEB3 DNA Browser futhi.</translation>
<translation id="8697124171261953979">Iphinda ilawule ukuthi yiliphi ikhasi eliboniswayo uma uqala i-WEB3 DNA Browser noma usesho kusuka ku-Omnibox.</translation>
<translation id="4220559821674570264">Lena yi-WEB3 DNA Browser yakho</translation>
<translation id="8072998028605263569">Uma uvala wonke amawindi e-WEB3 DNA Browser, amakhukhi nedatha yesayithi iyasulwa ngokuzenzakalelayo</translation>
<translation id="6903751245620697304"><ph name="BEGIN_BOLD" />Uzokhishwa ngemvume kumasayithi amaningi<ph name="END_BOLD" /> lapho uvala i-WEB3 DNA Browser. Uma ukuvumelanisa kuvaliwe, nawe <ph name="BEGIN_BOLD" />uzokhishwa ngemvume kumasevisi e-Google naku-WEB3 DNA Browser<ph name="END_BOLD" />.</translation>
<translation id="7277260025828649281">I-WEB3 DNA Browser idinga imvume ukuze ifinyelele kukhamera yakho nemakrofoni yaleli sayithi</translation>
<translation id="8833697763442816810">Isistimu ye-ChromiumOS</translation>
<translation id="7404934872971073925"><ph name="BEGIN_BOLD" />Iyiphi idatha esetshenziswayo:<ph name="END_BOLD" /> Umlando wakho wokubhrawuza, irekhodi lamasayithi owavakashele usebenzisa i-WEB3 DNA Browser kule divayisi.</translation>
<translation id="8862326446509486874">Awunawo amalungelo afanele wokufakwa okukuleveli yesistimu. Zama ukuqalisa isifaki futhi njengomlawuli.</translation>
<translation id="8304007095757244531">Uma kunjalo, sicela uhlele iphasiwedi yakho elondoloziwe ku-WEB3 DNA Browser ukuze ifane nephasiwedi yakho entsha.</translation>
<translation id="8897323336392112261">Iphinda ilayishe ukuthi yiliphi ikhasi eliboniswayo uma uqala i-WEB3 DNA Browser noma uchofoza kunkinobho ye-Ikhaya.</translation>
<translation id="257978004891740263">I-WEB3 DNA Browser izama ukubonisa amaphasiwedi. Thayipha iphasiwedi yakho ye-Windows ukuze uvumele lokhu.</translation>
<translation id="7500894618301979366">I-WEB3 DNA Browser ingasikisela izinto ozithakaselayo ngokusekelwe kumlando wakho wokubhrawuza kusukela emavikini ambalwa adlule. Lolu lwazi luhlala kudivayisi yakho.</translation>
<translation id="3731673200617615844">Ayikwazi ukubuyekeza i-WEB3 DNA Browser</translation>
<translation id="1787382483918628946">Ilogo ye-WEB3 DNA Browser Enterprise</translation>
<translation id="8986207147630327271">Ungeza iphrofayela yomsebenzi kulesi siphequluli futhi unikeza umlawuli wakho ulawulo olungaphezulu nje kwephrofayela yomsebenzi.</translation>
<translation id="8867249455463470821">Ukuze senze i-WEB3 DNA Browser iphephe, sikhubaza isandiso esilandelayo esingafakiwe kuhlu lwe-<ph name="IDS_EXTENSION_WEB_STORE_TITLE" /> futhi kungenzeka singezwe ngaphandle kolwazi lakho.</translation>
<translation id="8879833215600767638">Ngena ngemvume ku-WEB3 DNA Browser</translation>
<translation id="853293422536067733">I-WEB3 DNA Browser ayikho kudethi</translation>
<translation id="325086175188777548">{0,plural, =1{I-WEB3 DNA Browser izoqalisa kabusha phakathi kwehora}one{I-WEB3 DNA Browser izoqalisa kabusha emahoreni angu-#}other{I-WEB3 DNA Browser izoqalisa kabusha emahoreni angu-#}}</translation>
<translation id="8024211601023847048">Ukuze uthole izibuyekezo zesikhathi esizayo ze-WEB3 DNA Browser, uzodinga i-Windows 10 noma yakamuva. Le khompyutha isebenzisa i-Windows 8.1.</translation>
<translation id="2383920618768832592">Vula isixhumanisi ku&amp;thebhu entsha ye-WEB3 DNA Browser</translation>
<translation id="911206726377975832">Phinda ususe idatha yakho yokudlulisa amehlo?</translation>
<translation id="3209098675401285328">Phakathi nezivivinyo, ungakwazi ukubona nokususa izihloko onentshisekelo kuzo ezisetshenziswa amasayithi ukuze uboniswe izikhangiso. I-WEB3 DNA Browser izolinganisa intshisekelo yakho ngokusekelwe kumlando wakho wakamuva wokubhrawuza.</translation>
<translation id="3219820530884298089">Umlawuli wesistimu yakho ulungise i-WEB3 DNA Browser ukuthi ivule esinye isiphequluli ukufinyelela i-<ph name="TARGET_URL_HOSTNAME" />.</translation>
<translation id="3490070383213151269">Qalisa kabusha ukuze ubuyekeze i-&amp;WEB3 DNA Browser</translation>
